title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 21 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 21 2022
description:
With GOP board expanding, Red Wave threatens to become a Red Tsunami. Clay says, "It's a good day to be on Team Red." More lies: Biden takes credit for supposedly plunging deficit. Polls show majority of Americans now realize, as Buck says, "BLM made everything worse for everyone." MSNBC's Scarborough claims crime is worse in red states. Musk plans to fire 75% of Twitter employees. Report: Biden administration looking for ways to stop Musk Twitter sale for "national security" reasons.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
